high_descs: Turn left for six steps, turn left again and walk forward to the couch and stop.
Pick up the red keys from the end table.
Turn around and walk five steps, take a right and walk five steps, turn left and face the TV desk.
Put the keys in the open space just below the desktop on the left side of the desk, and put the keys on the front right side of the space.
Turn right and walk eight steps and turn to face the side of the chair.
Pick up the keys from the chair.
Turn left and take four steps, turn right for one step, turn left for five steps and turn left to face the desk.
Put the key to the left of the keys already in the left space below the desktop.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of key in an empty space under the TV desk.

high_descs: Turn left then left again to the table beside the couch.
Grab the keys from the table.
Turn around the walk right then left to the dresser.
Place the keys on the dresser.
Turn left and walk to the closest black chair.
Grab the keys from that chair.
Turn around back to the dresser.
Place the second set of keys to the left of the first set.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the black chairs and walk to the round glass table.
Pick up the set of keys on the left side of the table.
Turn around and walk to the black television stand against the wall.
Put the keys on the top left shelf on the television stand.
Turn left and walk to the black chair on the left.
Pick up the set of keys from the middle of the chair.
Turn left and walk to the television stand on the left.
Put the set of keys on the top shelf to the left of the other set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Place two sets of keys on a television stand.
